  <span id="freeText11934646687551551153" style="display:none">James Bond on speed! If you want to travel to Antarctica, to be shot at with pistols, rocket launchers and crossbows and wrestle with killer whales and (navy) seals, this is the book. Hilariously over the top. A total page turner. Action, action, action from the very first page and it never stops until the end. I kept thinking, this can not be topped and then something else crazy happened... I kept giving sound bites to my fellow travellers in the minibus in the morning and they just thought I was bonkers.... If you love action and suspense, don't miss this! Suspend belief and enjoy a mega rollercoaster ride! </span>
